  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK404">
<l>kallātā ṉoṭpaṅ kaḻiyanaṉ ṟāyiṉum</l>
<l>koḷḷā raṟivuṭai yār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Although the natural knowledge of an unlearned man may be very good, the wise will not accept for true knowledge.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
